                <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
                <p class="info-pane">Fotio was created to help photographers and clients have an easy, hassle free meeting and quoting experience. Our goal is to reduce the amount of time people spend googling "Top photographers in Toronto" only to have to sift though endless websites and contact pages - struggling to find one that fits their needs. We want to provide a platform that empowers both the client and photographer and creates a mutually beneficial transaction. Take the headache out of finding the perfect photographer for your next big event, and let them come to you.</p></br>
