                <h2>Photographers & Fotio</h2>
                <p class="info-pane">The photography industry is booming and becoming more and more saturated with grass roots photographers competeing in a race to the bottom. Our platform charges a fee to help root out those that treat this more as a hobby than a profession. Our hope is to create a comprehensive directory of top notch professional photographers in Ontario. However, unlike some other photography market places, we do not charge on a per quote basis. A yearly subscription fee allows you to quote as many jobs as you like, host your portfolio and gives you access to all future features.</p>
